# Segmentation

This module generates pose vector from given text.

## Launching

- **build & run module**

    ```
    docker build -t model .
    sudo docker run -it -p 5004:5004 --rm  --name model_running model
    ```

    reading logs:
    ```
    docker logs -f model_running
    ```

    stopping:
    ```
    docker stop model_running
    ```


## Usage

```
curl -X POST -d "" "http://localhost:2488/get_segmentation/"
```

answer:
```
{
   "body": ""
}
```
